[options="header",cols="10%,10%,10%,70%"]
|======

| Property
| Mandatory 
| Type
| Description


| x
| no
| number
| The horizontal position of the focal point. The value is a factor of the image width. The value 0.5 is the center of the image.  Default: *0.0*.

| y
| no
| number
| The vertical position of the focal point. The value is a factor of the image height. The value 0.5 is the center of the image.  Default: *0.0*.

|======
